        public void printModelDetail​(Student student)
        print detail of student (student name, matric number, major and year).
        参数:
        student - This passes in the model(student) into the method. the details of student will be printed using the getter of student

      • printCoursesRegistered

        public void printCoursesRegistered​(Set<Index> indexes)
        print the courses registered by a student. if the student is not registered for any index, "Not registered to any course yet" will be printed.
        参数:
        indexes - This passes in the all the indexes that a student registered.

      • printOnWaitlist

        public void printOnWaitlist​(Set<Index> indexes)
        print the courses that a student is put on waitlist. if the student is not on waitlist for any index, "Not registered on any waitlist" will be printed.
        参数:
        indexes - This passes in the all the indexes that a student is on waitlist

      • saveStudentInfo

        public void saveStudentInfo​(Student student)
        save the info of a student to student_information.csv. registered and waitlisted indexes are first concatenated into a string representation.
        参数:
        student - This passes in the student whose information will be saved in this method
